			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64109247">		
		on Wednesday December 27, 2023 @12:09PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23173843&amp;cid=64109247">#64109247</a>)
		<small><a href="http://rm-f.net/" title="http://rm-f.net/" class="user_homepage_display">Homepage</a>
